I like the movie because it was real, no holds barred, make you not want to go to prison after seeing this

I saw this movie, although not in it's entirety some years ago, and I had been looking for it for a long time. Well I finally found it, and it is really a good movie, and you would not expect the ending to be what it is if you've never seen it. Be forewarned, if you're offended by same sex love scenes, there's one or two in this movie; but then it's a women's prison movie and that's a part of making the movie realistic, because that kind of activity does go on.
